            ],
            "pathId": 3403793369231161624,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "『天皇賞（秋）』も、\nその先の『ジャパンカップ』も……\n『宝塚記念』より、派手になりそうだ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "voiceIdx": 55,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それはワクワクするな……！",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "それはワクワクするね……！",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 59,
                    "pathId": 2501867581836905700
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 116,
                    "pathId": 7455127607279418908
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3482140009128998455,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ハハッ、子どもみたいな顔してら。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 8446587225996276748
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -5741778241103462703
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4637365530899969189,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "他愛ない会話の中で、ふと思う。\n秋が深まるにつれて、\n彼女を中心に何かが集まっているとしたら――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": 9139791889497290121
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -4756281394536466523
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1024844372833825757,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……その果てにあるレースでは、\n何が起きるのだろう。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -1806693067263490560
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -3043456895671773772
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5296306095720979905,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして、\n最も多くの縁が集まるであろう舞台は――",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 76,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": 8503265106500967632
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": 3090115126816943199
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5296542204694535327,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "――よし、気分がノッてきたぞ。",
            "enText": "",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "お、じゃあやっぱりトレーニングを――",
                    "enText": "",
                    "nextBlock": 17
